ciples, if the officers of a legal entity sign a contract binding that lega=
l entity to do something, a later vote by a Discord chat to reject the cont=
ract doesn=E2=80=99t carry much weight. But I think a lot of people who are=
 really into crypto would disagree.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here=E2=
