 stuff</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On May 20, Honey Ba=
rrel, whose online bio describes them only as a =E2=80=9Cvanquisher of non-=
frens,=E2=80=9D woke up and chose chaos. They=E2=80=99re a member of Merit =
Circle DAO, a decentralized autonomous organization worth over $370 million=
