 one of the first ones to post their transparency &amp; accountability thre=
ad to share and create a dialogue with the community.</p><p style=3D"margin=
: 16px 0;">After taking in the proposal and observing the community=E2=80=
=99s feedback, Merit Circle Ltd reached out to Yield Guild Games. Yield Gui=
