None of the parties had to settle, but both parties chose the constructive =
path to help Merit Circle move forward.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">Everything is legal enough (because they settled), but still unne=
rving. Contracts with DAOs don=E2=80=99t entirely count, if the DAO can rej=
