 the vote of the DAO by saying =E2=80=9Cwell we signed a contract.=E2=80=9D=
</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">By the way, one is tempted to say, like, =
=E2=80=9Csmart contracts on the blockchain can solve this=E2=80=9D? Like in=
