=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">got in trouble with the SEC yesterday</a> for=
 an assortment of awkwardnesses. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/28141627.276598/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9saXRpZ2F0aW9uL2Fk=
bWluLzIwMjIvMzQtOTUxMjcucGRm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3d8779f3" itemprop=3D=
"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
